{"tid":2456301,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–蘋果皮","createTime":"2021-03-21T21:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:53:33.000Z","uid":38861,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"715efba5b33ad0d01651e22ff643e86e4785264b","tid":2456301,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T21:56:39.000Z","msg":"吃蘋果的時候，大家會否去皮，不把蘋果皮放進口裡呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgQhK71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgQhK71.jpg&h=059b7c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）不少研究均指出蘋果皮含有豐富的化學物質類Polyphenol，有科學家更特意利用乾蘋果皮作研究，發現內裡至少有26%的物質均為Polyphenol;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2noFGo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2noFGo.png&h=29ecde71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而Polyphenol則一直被譽為有著抗氧化及能夠抑止發炎的功用。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）有科學家利用DSS化學物在老鼠身上催化結腸炎(colitis)，並每日為老鼠餵食蘋果皮，份量為400mg/kg。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRaNnUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRaNnUV.png&h=ad1a77d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n化學物所造成的結腸炎情況，在進食蘋果皮的作用下，其外觀與正常的結腸並無太大分別。<br />\n<br />\n科學家亦發現進食蘋果皮的老鼠，其腸道細菌品種亦有著輕微的改變。<br />\n<br />\n究竟蘋果皮抵禦結腸炎的效果是否100%歸功於Polyphenol，暫時未可下一個確切的結論。<br />\n<br />\n但宏觀來看，若能清除蘋果皮上的農藥（如有），吃下蘋果皮大有可能對身體會有正面效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=130ff403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=570bb57a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3553108/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3553108%2F&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c106bfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3553108/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://portlandpress.com/clinsci/article-abstract/130/23/2217/71485/Apple-peel-polyphenols-a-key-player-in-the?redirectedFrom=fulltext\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fportlandpress.com%2Fclinsci%2Farticle-abstract%2F130%2F23%2F2217%2F71485%2FApple-peel-polyphenols-a-key-player-in-the%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=984907b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://portlandpress.com/clinsci/article-abstract/130/23/2217/71485/Apple-peel-polyphenols-a-key-player-in-the?redirectedFrom=fulltext</a>"},{"pid":"e08ee58e41fbc3d32dcc5c0465485c88a7120527","tid":2456301,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T21:57:49.000Z","msg":"樓豬咁夜開po冇人流㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6892c0482b37cb8af323f0030cdc9563e57586","tid":2456301,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e08e